msgctxt "Talk_0012"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I want to visit the land in the sky by\n"
"<2.se_co>balloon<3.re_co>.<4.pa> Then, I'm going to ride a really\n"
"big bird. Yep, that's my dream!\n"
"<5.so>Thank you, mister!<6.pa> This is a <7.se_co>treasure<8.re_co>\n"
"from the sky! <9.pa>Here, take it!"
msgstr ""

